<subSubSection id="C3590FD3154DE81301858E48B505FE7C" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BFC5C58154DE81301858E48B505FE7C" blockId="7.[151,1436,282,561]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">
<emphasis id="B937804A154DE81301858E48B7BBFEA0" bold="true" box="[151,249,282,308]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Remark</emphasis>
. The 
<typeStatus id="54F8E2FA154DE813002A8E49B62AFEA1" box="[312,360,283,309]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">type</typeStatus>
specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4327DB154DE81300E98E49B5E6FEA0" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Mabille" authorityYear="1879" box="[507,676,282,308]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Bizone" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grandis">
<emphasis id="B937804A154DE81300E98E49B5E6FEA0" box="[507,676,282,308]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Bizone grandis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not located since 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD221A9154DE813028E8E49B31AFEA0" author="Hampson, G. F." box="[924,1112,282,309]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" pagination="1 - 590" refId="ref3831" refString="Hampson, G. F. (1900) Catalogue of the Arctiadae (Nolinae, Lithosianae) in the British Museum. Catalogue of the Lepidoptera Phalaenae in the British Museum, 2, 1 - 590." type="journal article" year="1900">Hampson (1900)</bibRefCitation>
illustrated it (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD221A9154DE81305E38E48B2D5FEA1" author="Toulgoet, H. de" box="[1265,1431,282,309]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" pagination="178 - 183" refId="ref4201" refString="Toulgoet, H. de (1957) Note pour servir a la revision systematique des Arctiidae malgaches (Lep.). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 61, 178 - 183. [in French]" type="journal article" year="1957">Toulgoët 1957</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD221A9154DE81301858E6CB6D9FECC" author="Viette, P. &amp; Fletcher, D. S." box="[151,411,318,344]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" pagination="389 - 425" refId="ref4286" refString="Viette, P. &amp; Fletcher, D. S. (1968) The types of Lepidoptera Heterocera described by P. Mabille. Bulletin of the British Museum of natural History, Entomology, 21, 389 - 425." type="journal article" year="1968">Viette &amp; Fletcher 1968</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD221A9154DE81300B58E6CB57DFECC" author="Karisch, T." box="[423,575,318,344]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" pagination="39 - 197" refId="ref3896" refString="Karisch, T. (2013) Taxonomic revision of the African Cyana - species (Lepidoptera: Arctiidae, Lithosiinae) (pls. 15 - 19). Esperiana, 18, 39 - 197." type="journal article" year="2013">Karisch 2013</bibRefCitation>
) and is probably lost. The specimen illustrated by Hampson (
<figureCitation id="137840DD154DE81305E28E6CB270FECD" box="[1264,1330,318,345]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–8" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1896,1920]" captionTargetBox="[160,1435,179,1860]" captionTargetId="figure-16@4.[151,1435,179,1870]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–8. Cyana spp.: adults. Depositories of specimens: 1–3, 5 and 6 in ZSM; 4 in NHMUK (©); 8 in MWM/ZSM. Figure 7 is given after Hampson (1900)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4416423" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4416423/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
) is externally identical to 
<taxonomicName id="4C4327DB154DE81300448E31B6FDFEE8" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1859" box="[342,447,355,381]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Bizone" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arama">
<emphasis id="B937804A154DE81300448E31B6FDFEE8" box="[342,447,355,381]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">C. arama</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="137840DD154DE81300DC8E30B54CFEE8" box="[462,526,354,380]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–8" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1896,1920]" captionTargetBox="[160,1435,179,1860]" captionTargetId="figure-16@4.[151,1435,179,1870]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–8. Cyana spp.: adults. Depositories of specimens: 1–3, 5 and 6 in ZSM; 4 in NHMUK (©); 8 in MWM/ZSM. Figure 7 is given after Hampson (1900)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4416423" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4416423/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
) and, taking into account the absence of any other externally similar species found neither from 
<collectingCountry id="F3541CC8154DE813003E8ED4B6F7FE34" box="[300,437,390,416]" name="Madagascar" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
, nor from other regions of Sub-Saharan Africa and Asia as well, I have no choice but to admit that the Mabille’s 
<typeStatus id="54F8E2FA154DE81300B58EF9B695FE51" box="[423,471,427,453]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">type</typeStatus>
specimen was mislabeled and here I synonymize 
<taxonomicName id="4C4327DB154DE81305118EF8B31BFE50" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Mabille" authorityYear="1879" box="[1027,1113,426,452]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Bizone" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grandis">
<emphasis id="B937804A154DE81305118EF8B31BFE50" box="[1027,1113,426,452]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">grandis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="4C4327DB154DE813058A8EF9B3A3FE50" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1859" box="[1176,1249,427,452]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Bizone" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arama">
<emphasis id="B937804A154DE813058A8EF9B3A3FE50" box="[1176,1249,427,452]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">arama</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and exclude this species from the fauna of 
<collectingCountry id="F3541CC8154DE81300AB8E9CB500FE7C" box="[441,578,462,488]" name="Madagascar" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
