<collectingCountry id="F3541CC8154DE81303878EA0B58DFD98" box="[661,719,498,524]" name="India" pageId="7" pageNumber="383">India</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFD221A9154DE81303CE8EA0B4DFFD98" author="Singh, N. &amp; Volynkin, A. V. &amp; Kirti, J. S. &amp; Datta, H. S. &amp; Ivanova, M. S." box="[732,925,498,524]" pageId="7" pageNumber="383" pagination="1 - 93" refId="ref4068" refString="Singh, N., Volynkin, A. V., Kirti, J. S., Datta, H. S. &amp; Ivanova, M. S. (2020) A review of the genus Cyana Walker, 1854 from India, with descriptions of five new species and three new subspecies (Lepidoptera: Erebidae: Arctiinae: Lithosiini). Zootaxa, 4738 (1), 1 - 93. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4738.1.1" type="journal article" year="2020">
Singh 
